wpt.desc: Just Hangin' by StarQ, Traditional Cache (1.5/1.5)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Just Hangin'
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: <font size="+2" color="#660033">Cache smaller than a breadbox and just smaller than a 33mm canister.</font>
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
Just Hangin' is a micro cache located in Marinelli Park. Please be sure to visit the memorial.

Parking located at N40°00.321, W075°41.759.

Bring a pen or pencil to make your log entry with.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: If you can't find me, check to see if I'm still Just Hangin' on the east side.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Had a little finding this one, but we got it. We were looking in the wrong place.
